    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-11-18T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-11-18T00:00:00-05:00" n="464" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d464">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to
                                Señor <persName type="to">Romero</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-11-18">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 18,
                                    1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to acknowledge the
                            receipt of your note of the 15th instant, touching a robbery committed
                            at Las Palomas, and the escape of the perpetrators into the United
                            States; and also regarding the alleged organization of a band near
                            Silver City, N. Mex., for similar operations in your country.</p>
                <p>I have addressed the Secretary of War and the governor of New Mexico with
                            a view to preventing the outrages you apprehend.</p>
                <p>Accept, etc,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">W. Q. Gresham</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
